name: FRAGMENT #4: COGITATION
description:
All things that happened this year hit me so hard, and the pain still lingers in the chest. But I realized, the comedy that I've survived, the time that I've wasted, will be a seed that will be growing up.

And then? What's next?
I don't know, my friend. The only thing I know is life must go on.

The last part of "Fragments of Fur". (4/4)
